params.812: Reach level 10 in the Ranged skill.
params.813: Ensure you have a Ranged weapon for your level with usable ammo. Cows and Farmers around Lumbridge are suitable targets to fight.
params.814: Take some food to keep your hitpoints high.|Cows and Farmers around Lumbridge are suitable targets to fight.|Cows drop hides that can be turned into leather for Crafting xp.|Arrows which don't break can be picked up from the ground.|Accurate fires arrows with a higher chance to hit.|Rapid fires arrows at a faster rate.|Longrange fires arrows further and gives Defence xp.
params.823: Use obstacles when using Ranged combat to avoid taking damage.
